<HEADLINE>
<P>
AIDS TESTING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
There is one fact neglected in comparing infections with hepatitis B and HIV in 
the editorial "The Illogic of Secret AIDS Testing" (Feb. 21). 
</P>
<P>
There is a vaccine available to prevent hepatitis B. There is as yet no vaccine 
to prevent HIV. 
</P>
<P>
SYLVAIN FRIBOURG, M.D. 
</P>
<P>
Panorama City 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
