<TEXT>
<P>
Apple Computer Inc. has officially announced the resignation of its executive 
in charge of new product development, Jean-Louis Gassee. The resignation was 
expected. Earlier this month, Apple Chairman John Sculley said he would take 
charge of new products at the Cupertino, Calif., personal computer maker, a 
function that Gasse has handled for the past five years. 
</P>
