<HEADLINE>
<P>
MARKET WATCH; 
</P>
<P>
WEEKLY SCORECARD; 
</P>
<P>
STOCK GROUP WINNERS &amp; LOSERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
