makes himself presentable in front of a cameraman's mirror before he goes on 
the air on the cable show "Cypress: Your City, Your Police," a local version of 
"America's Most Wanted." Spernak had just hurried into the studio from some 
frantic real-life police work. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
