<TEXT>
<P>
The Spurs today filled their 12th roster spot by signing free agent Reggie 
Williams, a Clippers' first-round draft choice in 1987. 
</P>
<P>
Williams was signed for the rest of the season, according to a statement issued 
by the Spurs. 
</P>
